222
00:10:53,518 --> 00:10:55,102
I need to talk to you.

223
00:10:55,169 --> 00:10:57,304
You want to talk
about how things played out,

224
00:10:57,355 --> 00:11:00,724
but the place to do that
is somewhere more private.

225
00:11:00,809 --> 00:11:04,278
You didn't just come through
on the merger.

226
00:11:04,345 --> 00:11:05,946
You bluffed Hardman,

227
00:11:06,013 --> 00:11:08,315
turned Monica Eton,

228
00:11:08,366 --> 00:11:09,616
and put us over the top
on Folsom Foods.

229
00:11:09,684 --> 00:11:11,985
Now that's a lot
of coming through in the clutch.

230
00:11:12,036 --> 00:11:14,321
And I wouldn't have saved
your ass

231
00:11:14,372 --> 00:11:17,741
if I didn't think
you deserved to be here.

232
00:11:17,826 --> 00:11:18,992
I don't know
what to say.

233
00:11:19,043 --> 00:11:20,911
Well, the usual response is
"thank you."

234
00:11:20,995 --> 00:11:22,296
The usual road
to getting here

235
00:11:22,363 --> 00:11:24,331
doesn't involve
stabbing someone in the back.

236
00:11:24,382 --> 00:11:27,551
Doesn't it?

237
00:11:29,671 --> 00:11:31,338
When I was 16,

238
00:11:31,389 --> 00:11:33,307
I came home,
my mother sat me down,

239
00:11:33,374 --> 00:11:35,476
and said my parents
were separating.

240
00:11:35,543 --> 00:11:38,095
Trial basis.

241
00:11:38,179 --> 00:11:41,064
But the good news was
she was going to get me a car

242
00:11:41,149 --> 00:11:42,683
to help with my sister.

243
00:11:42,734 --> 00:11:46,353
All my friends talked about
how lucky I was to have it.

244
00:11:46,404 --> 00:11:49,740
I hated that car.

245
00:11:49,824 --> 00:11:52,910
Every time I got in it, I--

246
00:11:52,994 --> 00:11:54,912
it just reminded me.

247
00:11:54,996 --> 00:11:57,030
Why are you telling me this?

248
00:11:57,081 --> 00:11:59,166
Because five years later,

249
00:11:59,233 --> 00:12:03,570
that same car got me to Harvard,
which led me here.

250
00:12:03,621 --> 00:12:05,756
So you can think
of this office

251
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:09,092
as a reminder
of what you did to Harvey

252
00:12:09,177 --> 00:12:12,129
or as a symbol
of what you can accomplish

253
00:12:12,213 --> 00:12:14,298
at the firm.

254
00:12:14,382 --> 00:12:17,751
Now, do you still
have something to say?

255
00:12:17,802 --> 00:12:20,938
No.

256
00:12:21,022 --> 00:12:23,357
No, I don't.

257
00:12:26,027 --> 00:12:28,028
They ever get back together?

