267
00:12:56,257 --> 00:12:57,641
Our...What?

268
00:12:57,725 --> 00:12:58,725
Pens, Donna.

269
00:12:58,793 --> 00:13:00,143
The new quartermaster,

270
00:13:00,228 --> 00:13:03,630
